casebody.data:
Eddie Milton GAREY, Jr., petitioner,
v.
Andrew MANSUKEANI, Warden, et al. No. 16-8930. Supreme Court of the United States June 5, 2017. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ certiorari dismissed. See Rule 39.8. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
